<template>
    <slot></slot>
</template>

<script>

    export default{
        data(){
            return {
                rank: null
            }
        },
        mounted (){
            if (this.score < 250){
                this.rank = 'Ninja Fingers'
            }
            else if (this.score < 400) {
                this.rank = 'Rapid Reflexes'
            }
        }
    }
</script>


<style>
</style>
